# Not committed: vite/rolldown ship platform-specific native binaries as
# optional deps, and npm's lockfile install (npm ci / npm install with a
# lockfile) leaves the wrong-platform binary out on CI/Netlify
# (https://github.com/npm/cli/issues/4828). A fresh `npm install` resolves the
# correct binary per platform; web deps are pinned to exact versions so this
# stays deterministic.
package-lock.json

# Go (cli-go): build output + the synced copy of core/feedback.json
packages/cli-go/bin
packages/cli-go/internal/password/feedback.json

